You came.

41
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:02,040
Long time no see, Seung Gyu.

42
00:05:03,500 --> 00:05:05,450
How are you feeling?

43
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:18,520
Is anyone there? Hello?

44
00:05:27,690 --> 00:05:30,840
There's no one to save you.

45
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:35,410
There's no point in screaming like that, I mean.

46
00:05:36,390 --> 00:05:42,190
I find it to be a shame you ended up this way,

47
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:46,050
