48
00:05:46,050 --> 00:05:49,970
If you come with me willingly,

49
00:05:49,970 --> 00:05:53,000
I'll compensate you fully.

50
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:57,440
You told me once that you wanted to go somewhere far away.

51
00:05:57,440 --> 00:06:00,190
I'll help you with that.

52
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:03,050
Do you think I'd believe what you say?

53
00:06:03,050 --> 00:06:04,450
You have to.

54
00:06:04,450 --> 00:06:07,200
Do you think you doing this

55
00:06:08,260 --> 00:06:11,940
